  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EПредприятие plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tУсловия",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Отмена your subscription at any Время through your platform's account sНастройки",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will не apply to your current billing period.",
