  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Здоровье data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Конфиденциальность Policy, which is incorporated into these Условия by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Экспорт your data at any Время via the in-app Экспорт feature, and you may permanently Удалить your account and Все associated data via Настройки → Удалить Account.",
